1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,670
[Episode 33]

2
00:00:02,670 --> 00:00:03,310
Hey.

3
00:00:04,270 --> 00:00:05,990
One o'clock direction, one o'clock direction.

4
00:00:05,990 --> 00:00:06,230
Hmm.

5
00:00:06,230 --> 00:00:07,430
He looks really good.

6
00:00:10,070 --> 00:00:11,800
Just like a Korean heartthrob.

7
00:00:12,150 --> 00:00:13,390
I must have accumulated good karma for several lifetimes

8
00:00:13,390 --> 00:00:14,920
to deserve a face like that.

9
00:00:15,670 --> 00:00:16,350
Hey.

10
00:00:16,950 --> 00:00:18,080
