12
00:00:21,430 --> 00:00:22,560
What are you talking about?

13
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:24,820
You're drunk after just that little bit?

14
00:00:24,950 --> 00:00:25,430
Yeah.

15
00:00:25,870 --> 00:00:27,190
You get drunk way too easily.

16
00:00:27,190 --> 00:00:29,270
Do you think I look handsome?

17
00:00:29,870 --> 00:00:32,270
If you covered your face, you'd be perfect.

18
00:00:33,070 --> 00:00:33,990
Idiot.

19
00:00:36,670 --> 00:00:37,190
But...

20
00:00:38,190 --> 00:00:39,250
I'm leaving first.

21
00:00:41,670 --> 00:00:42,190
Go ahead.

22
00:00:42,190 --> 00:00:43,150
I'm grown up now.

23
00:00:43,150 --> 00:00:44,150
I can take care of myself.

24
00:00:44,150 --> 00:00:44,510
Hmm.

25
00:00:44,910 --> 00:00:46,150
I'll help you take care of him.

26
00:00:46,150 --> 00:00:47,190
Just look, okay?

27
00:00:51,110 --> 00:00:51,950
Come on, come on.

28
00:00:51,950 --> 00:00:52,610
Come, come.

29
00:00:53,030 --> 00:00:54,030
Wait a second, hey.

30
00:00:54,030 --> 00:00:56,230
Here, this drink is yours, Bin.

31
00:00:56,990 --> 00:00:58,320
Specially made for you.

32
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:01,250
Drink it all up.

33
00:01:01,710 --> 00:01:02,710
Hmm.

34
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:07,870
Time to party.

35
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:09,789
Let's go.

36
00:01:10,870 --> 00:01:11,350
Hey.

37
00:01:12,830 --> 00:01:14,030
You're really drunk.

38
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:14,670
OK.

39
